Source.Name: swipl
Source.Summary: SWI-Prolog offers a comprehensive free Prolog environment
Source.Description: SWI-Prolog is a versatile implementation of the Prolog language. Its robust multi-threading, extended data types, unbounded arithmetic and Unicode representation of text allow for natural representation of documents (e.g., XML, JSON, RDF) and exchange of data with other programming paradigms.
